1
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:05,799
Lin Niannian's body

2
00:01:06,159 --> 00:01:06,879
We found it

3
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,200
Fang Qiu confessed

4
00:01:21,079 --> 00:01:22,920
The body was buried in an abandoned factory in the suburbs

5
00:01:26,359 --> 00:01:28,000
Tan Tian, Zhao Qihai, A Si

6
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,120
They've all been arrested

7
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:31,280
Li Ren

8
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:34,200
The crimes you committed

9
00:01:34,359 --> 00:01:35,640
We will investigate every single one

10
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:42,040
But I'd like you to tell me

11
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,079
Your biological father

12
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:45,799
And the deaths of your adoptive parents

13
00:01:46,879 --> 00:01:48,040
Are they also connected to you?

14
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:53,239
You're asking me?

15
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:56,680
Aren't you going to investigate every single one?

16
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,439
Investigate it yourself

17
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,599
You're a smart person

18
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:10,680
Confessing is in your best interest

19
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:21,919
You should know that very well

20
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,319
You are a key member of Zhao Qishan's criminal gang

21
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,599
Not only for the murders of Zhao Qishan and Chen Fang

22
00:02:26,719 --> 00:02:27,759
must you bear criminal responsibility

23
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,199
but everything that passed through your hands

24
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,599
and the victims you controlled

25
00:02:30,919 --> 00:02:31,800
are all linked to you

26
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:36,599
Alright

27
00:02:38,439 --> 00:02:39,319
Then let me ask you again

28
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,960
You captured Lin Niannian on purpose, didn't you?

29
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,680
We've investigated and verified

30
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,159
that your relationship with her in high school

31
00:02:48,919 --> 00:02:49,879
was quite complicated

32
00:02:55,039 --> 00:02:56,520
Lin Niannian, you really are a witch

33
00:02:56,719 --> 00:02:57,639
Always stealing men

34
00:02:57,879 --> 00:02:58,879
You knew Halun was my boyfriend

35
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,360
Yet you steal him and go against me, huh?

36
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,719
How is it stealing?

37
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,439
Halun likes me

38
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:05,840
He wants to pursue me himself

39
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,919
Blame yourself for having no charm

40
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,159
You...

41
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:11,520
Don't move

42
00:03:11,719 --> 00:03:12,039
You witch

43
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:13,199
Li Ren, help me

44
00:03:13,439 --> 00:03:14,000
What are you doing? Let go

45
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:14,879
If you don't stop, I'll tell the teacher

46
00:03:14,879 --> 00:03:15,879
That's for stealing my boyfriend

47
00:03:16,159 --> 00:03:16,599
Don't move

48
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,280
You're not going anywhere

49
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,120
Are you okay?

50
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,280
What do we do now?

51
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,080
Teacher

52
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,280
What is going on here?

53
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,639
It's just like I told you on the phone.

54
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:43,639
Your daughter and her...

55
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:45,960
the two of them conspired...

56
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,639
to push their classmate Zhao Li...

57
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:49,280
down the stairs.

58
00:03:50,039 --> 00:03:50,960
I didn't do it!

59
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,360
She fell down by herself.

60
00:03:52,759 --> 00:03:53,479
You shut up.

61
00:03:53,719 --> 00:03:55,479
Zhao Li has been sent to the hospital now.

62
00:03:55,879 --> 00:03:56,879
Her parents have gone there too.

63
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,360
I advise you...

64
00:03:58,719 --> 00:04:00,120
to go to the hospital immediately to visit her.

65
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:02,199
Apologize properly to the family.

66
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,599
Pay whatever compensation is due.

67
00:04:03,879 --> 00:04:04,759
As for your daughter,

68
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,960
take her home first and discipline her well.

69
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:07,759
Okay.

70
00:04:07,919 --> 00:04:08,400
Regarding the punishment,

71
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,439
I will discuss it with the school board...

72
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:11,680
and notify you once we have a result.

73
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:13,759
Teacher...

74
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,879
Hurry up and apologize to the teacher!

75
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:17,680
Hurry!

76
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,040
Why should I apologize?

77
00:04:19,199 --> 00:04:20,480
She fell on her own, I didn't push her!

78
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:21,680
Why make me apologize?

79
00:04:23,399 --> 00:04:24,000
Teacher...

80
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,480
Li Ren.

81
00:04:28,959 --> 00:04:29,560
Li Ren.

82
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,839
Renren.

83
00:04:34,759 --> 00:04:36,279
Niannian cannot bear...

84
00:04:36,399 --> 00:04:38,399
the consequences of being expelled for pushing someone.

85
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,319
She can't handle such a blow.

86
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:42,040
Auntie begs you.

87
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:47,720
Take this responsibility on yourself.

88
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,480
I can give you money.

89
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:52,439
Yes, I can give you money.

90
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:55,120
I can also cover all of Zhao Li's medical bills.

91
00:04:55,519 --> 00:04:57,199
Whatever amount you want, discuss it with Auntie.

92
00:04:58,079 --> 00:05:00,000
You have no parents, no ties.

93
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,079
It doesn't matter for you.

94
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:03,000
But for Niannian, it won't do.

95
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,079
Fine.

96
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,439
I'll consider it.

97
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,160
I'll give you a figure.

98
00:05:10,759 --> 00:05:12,680
So, you agree?

99
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:14,079
Wait for my news.

100
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:17,839
Because of this incident,

101
00:05:18,639 --> 00:05:20,399
your entire life trajectory was affected.

102
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:23,079
So your hatred for Lin Niannian...

103
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,600
must have been planted from that moment.

104
00:05:26,839 --> 00:05:27,720
Coincidentally,

105
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,000
you met later in Tai Cheng.

106
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:32,759
At that time, you were under Zhao Qishan's control.

107
00:05:33,439 --> 00:05:35,680
You were completely crazy and chaotic.

108
00:05:40,279 --> 00:05:41,519
So you made your move on her, right?

109
00:05:41,959 --> 00:05:43,720
She brought it on herself.

110
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,480
She was vain.

111
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:50,079
That's why she fell into Fang Qiu's trap.

112
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,079
You've said so much.

113
00:06:03,639 --> 00:06:04,800
How is my sister?

114
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,360
Ran.

115
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:20,360
Ran.

116
00:06:24,199 --> 00:06:26,000
Save my sister, quickly!

117
00:06:26,839 --> 00:06:28,879
Save my sister!

118
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:45,439
I can only tell you...

119
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:49,480
that everyone who has done wrong...

120
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,639
must pay the price.

121
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,600
It's the same for everyone.

122
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:21,360
Sister.

123
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:24,399
Sister.

124
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,199
Sister.

125
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,560
I'm late.

126
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,120
I snuck out.

127
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,439
I understand.

128
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:35,600
After all, your adoptive parents are determined...

129
00:07:35,759 --> 00:07:36,959
not to let us interact.

130
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,800
They are just worried about me.

131
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,120
They don't mean anything else by it.

132
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,199
I understand.

133
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:43,560
For your sake,

134
00:07:44,079 --> 00:07:45,480
I can stand in the shadows.

135
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:50,759
I just hope you can...

136
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,279
be healthy,

137
00:07:52,879 --> 00:07:53,480
happy,

138
00:07:54,639 --> 00:07:56,680
and grow up carefree facing the sunshine.

139
00:07:59,959 --> 00:08:00,439
Sister,

140
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,800
when I graduate from college,

141
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:05,160
I will definitely go to Tai Cheng to find you.

142
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:06,639
We will live together.

143
00:08:06,959 --> 00:08:07,839
I'll be waiting.

144
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:10,439
We will stand side by side...

145
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,720
and live in the sunshine.

146
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,879
Inspector Qi, what are you thinking about?

147
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:50,440
Nothing.

148
00:08:54,039 --> 00:08:55,360
This was found at the Li family's old house.

149
00:09:32,759 --> 00:09:34,000
Mom!

150
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,240
Don't go!

151
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,200
I'll beat you to death!

152
00:09:37,759 --> 00:09:38,600
Beat you to death!

153
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:43,240
You two! Stop right there!

154
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:44,559
How dare you steal buns!

155
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,279
Call your dad.

156
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,000
Uncle has business with him.

157
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,799
The sun is finally out.

158
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,240
Yeah.

159
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,120
The rain will stop eventually.

160
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,559
Just like justice.

161
00:10:18,159 --> 00:10:19,320
It will never be absent.

162
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,559
I'm leaving Tai Cheng too.

163
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,799
Inspector Qi, the transfer order is in.

164
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,600
To Manchester or Yin Cheng?

165
00:10:31,919 --> 00:10:32,559
Hancheng.
